Initially my application crashed due to selection of the BucketQueueAssignmentPolicy. Obviously i had changed other default options like the
Archiver, and the politeness settings including max-retry and retry-del;ay and fetch-http-timeout. 

However after the application crashed i tried changing the queueAssignmentPolicy in a frtesh installation of heritrix-2.0 and i chose the profile basic-seed-sites crawl. But still the app crashed with the same errors. 

I also tried selecting optionally a BdbServerCache or a DefaultServerCache along with the BucketQueueAssignmentPolicy but to no avail. 

Pratyush







